text.tspan: Fish catch in the United Kingdom
Total annual landings – fish catch brought back to land – of bottom-living fish. This excludes shellfish.
Data source: Ruth Thurstan et al. (2010). The effects of 118 years of industrial fishing on UK bottom trawl fisheries. Nature
